Dan Gilvezan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dan_Gilvezan 0 Daniel John Gilvezan (born October 26, 1950) is an American actor, known for playing Peter Parker/Spider-Man in the 1981 animated series, Spider-Man and His Amazing Friends and Autobot Bumblebee, among others, in the original 1984-1987 Transformers series.
